Beseech - Discografia Completa

..:: Sobre/About ::..
Beseech foi uma banda de goth rock/gothic metal de Boreas, Suecia. O grupo se dividiu, e atualmente formaram duas outras bandas: TWDSO (tambem conhecida como Those We Dont Speak Of) e The Mary Major.

Beseech was the name of a goth rock/gothic metal band from Boreas, Sweden. The group has disbanded and have actually formed two other bands, TWDSO (also known as Those We Dont Speak Of) and The Mary Major.
